name: ACCEL
description: Accel Defi is a multi-utility token. A token that brings with it several real world utilities. From an escrow payment application, a decentralized exchange trading application, and P2E game development. In addition Accel Defi brings it's own launchpad and token accelerator allowing others to launch their own tokens with the safest of smart contracts. A conglomerate of resources for the cryptospace with an education wing to help teach users along the way.
